                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="how-it-works-card">
                            <div class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-user-edit fa-3x"></i></div>
                            <h5>1. Enter Details</h5>
                            <p>Provide basic details like age, income, and occupation to check eligibility.</p>
